We receive many good reputations from users.
- I could have never assumed that I can draw such a beautiful drawings on smartphones!

[Manga Features]
- Advanced text tool function featuring Vertical, Horizontal, Stroke, Font select, and Multiple text functions.

Text Transformer is a powerful and user-friendly application designed to transform text in various ways.
 With an intuitive interface and 14 unique transformation modes, the app is suitable for both personal and professional needs.

* Main Features

14 Transformation Modes

-  Mirror Text - Reverse entire text  
-  Reverse Text - Reverse text (similar to Mirror)  
-  Flip Text - Flip text (upside-down effect)  
-  Word Letters - Reverse letters within each word  
-  Word Order - Reverse the order of words  
-  Alternating - Alternating uppercase/lowercase letters  
-  Title Case - Capitalize the first letter of each word  
-  Camel Case - Convert to camelCase  
-  Snake Case - Convert to snake_case  
-  Vowel Only - Keep only vowels  
-  Consonant Only - Keep only consonants  
-  Palindrome - Create symmetrical text  
-  Binary - Convert to binary code  
-  Morse - Convert to Morse code

With Widgy, your home and lock screens become YOUR screens. Create any widget you can imagine to perfectly match your style. Get all the info you need, exactly how you want it, without the clutter.

You don’t need to be a pro designer. Just know what you want, and let your creativity flow. Add an element, pick a data source, throw on some effects, and place it where you want. Repeat until your widget is perfect, then assign it to a slot and drop it on your home screen. Voila!
